                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The vargouille distends its jaw awfully and emits an unnerving shriek. All creatures within 60 feet who can see and hear the vargouille must attempt a @Check[type:fortitude|dc:15] save.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is unaffected and is temporarily immune to Vargouille's Shriek for 24 hours.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Paralyzed] until the end of its next turn.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is paralyzed. It can attempt a new save at the end of each of its turns, and the DC cumulatively decreases by 1 on each such save.</p>"
